## Article content starts here

This can occur when sending an incorrect content-type header to the Gateway. Some utilities, such as curl, default to using Content-type:application/x-www-form-urlencoded. To address the issue ensure you are sending the Content-type:application/json



### Include code examples

```
curl -XPOST -d '{
        "messages": [
                {
                        "role": "user",
                        "content": "Why is the sky blue?"
                }
        ]
}' -H "Content-type:application/json" https://mygateway/api/v1

```
